    "body": "I was thinking about to implement on the router middleware level, but history.ts has setWindowTitle function. It won't be called if avoid the write method call.\r\nOn the other hand, fix on router manager level will prevent such issue with browser history for any other routers.. But in case of `popstate` event this issue related only to history router..\r\nHmm, I think I almost agree with you..)\r\nSo, should I do changes in the same branch/PR or we will keep the current commit?",
